
Ranger Help for: edge
=====================

SYNTAX:      edge <slash or pierce type weapon>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   6
BASE SP:     35 sp
SKILL TYPE:  aid

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to take a slash or pierce type weapon
and sharpen it to razor sharpness, significantly enhancing its
weapon class for a while. It requires a carried rock or stone rather
than just nearby terrain.

If you are in hills, mountains, or underground terrain, use 'quarry'
to gather a rock first.
